# ---- backend-dawn ----
# Build output, not source. The jar used to be committed, which meant it drifted
# from src/ silently (it needed a manual "重建 jar" commit to catch up) and could
# not even run from a checkout, since lib/ was ignored beside it. CI now builds
# both and uploads them as an artifact — that is what gets deployed.
# Third-party jars come from backend-dawn/dawn.toml's [java-deps], fetched from
# Maven by `dawn build`; dawn.toml is the single source of truth for versions.
backend-dawn/backend-dawn.jar
backend-dawn/lib/

# ---- Editor / OS ----
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
